<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - Hospital Management System</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <!-- Using a professional font from Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #0d6efd;
            --dark-bg: #1a1a2e;
            --light-bg: #f8f9fa;
            --text-light: #f0f0f0;
            --text-dark: #333;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--light-bg);
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }
        
        .navbar { background-color: var(--dark-bg); }
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(26,26,46,0.95), rgba(22,43,105,0.95)), url('/images/login.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: var(--text-light);
            padding: 6rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero h1 { font-weight: 700; }

        .section { padding: 4rem 0; }
        .section-title { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary-color); display: inline-block; }
        
        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            border: 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .feature-card:hover { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        .feature-card i { font-size: 3rem; color: var(--primary-color); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        
        .tech-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .tech-icon:hover { color: var(--primary-color); transform: scale(1.1); }
        
        .license-box { background-color: #e9ecef; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; border-radius: 5px; padding: 1.5rem; font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; max-height: 400px; overflow-y: auto; }
        
        .github-cta { background-color: var(--dark-bg); color: var(--text-light); }
        .github-cta .btn { transition: transform 0.2s ease; }
        .github-cta .btn:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }

        footer { background-color: var(--dark-bg); color: var(--text-light); padding: 2rem 0; text-align: center; }
        footer a { color: #fff; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-dark shadow-sm">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="/">Hospital Management System</a>
            <a class="nav-link text-white-50" href="/">Return to App</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="display-3">A Modern Vision for Healthcare Management</h1>
                <p class="lead col-lg-8 mx-auto">This project is more than code; it's a demonstration of building secure, scalable, and user-centric web applications from the ground up.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h2 class="section-title">Project Philosophy</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted">The core philosophy is to adhere to modern best practices in web development. This means prioritizing security through measures like password hashing and parameterized queries, ensuring data integrity with a relational database schema, and providing a clean, role-based user experience. The application is designed to be a professional portfolio piece and a learning tool for developers interested in full-stack JavaScript development.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
                    <i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill" style="font-size: 8rem; color: #e9ecef;"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section bg-white">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title text-center d-block mx-auto">Core Features</h2>
                <div class="row g-4 mt-3">
                    <div class="col-lg-4"><div class="feature-card"><i class="bi bi-person-lock"></i><h5>Role-Based Security</h5><p class="text-muted">Distinct, protected portals for Administrators and Users.</p></div></div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4"><div class="feature-card"><i class="bi bi-person-lines-fill"></i><h5>Patient Management</h5><p class="text-muted">Securely add, view, update, and delete patient records.</p></div></div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4"><div class="feature-card"><i class="bi bi-calendar2-check"></i><h5>Appointment System</h5><p class="text-muted">Intuitive forms for booking and managing appointments.</p></div></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section container">
            <h2 class="section-title text-center d-block mx-auto">Technology Powering the System</h2>
            <div class="row g-5 mt-4 text-center">
                <div class="col"><i class="tech-icon bi-filetype-js"></i><p>JavaScript (ES6+)</p></div>
                <div class="col"><i class="tech-icon bi-node-plus-fill"></i><p>Node.js</p></div>
                <div class="col"><i class="tech-icon bi-box-seam-fill"></i><p>Express.js</p></div>
                <div class="col"><i class="tech-icon bi-server"></i><p>MariaDB/MySQL</p></div>
                <div class="col"><i class="tech-icon bi-bootstrap-fill"></i><p>Bootstrap 5</p></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="github-cta text-center py-5">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">View the Source</h2>
                <p class="lead mb-4">This project is fully open-source. Explore the code, learn from the architecture, or contribute.</p>
                <a href="https://github.com/ItsAsh95/HospitalMS" class="btn btn-light btn-lg fw-bold px-4" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="bi bi-github me-2"></i>View on GitHub</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section container">
            <h2 class="section-title">License</h2>
            <p>This project is licensed under the permissive <b>MIT License</b>. You are free to use, modify, and distribute this software for any purpose, with the only condition being the inclusion of the original copyright notice.</p>
